OL,2,MControlling Drones with Satellites
OL,4,CMolly Scarlet
OL,5,CFri 18:40-19:10
OL,6,CStage B
OL,8,GOwnership and usage of drones has
OL,9,Gskyrocketed over recent years, with
OL,10,Gthe US Federal Aviation Administration
OL,11,G(FAA) estimating that 8% of people in
OL,12,Gthe US own a drone (nearly 27 million
OL,13,Gpeople) and the UK Civil Aviation
OL,14,GAuthority stating that there are over
OL,15,G500,000 drones registered in the UK
OL,16,Gfor commercial or recreational use. At
OL,17,Gthe same time, satellite usage for all
OL,18,Gkinds of purposes has also increased
OL,19,Gdrastically — most famously with the
OL,20,Gintroduction of Starlink broadband
OL,22,D]CEMFFAX: The world at your fingertips\
